  "body_chunks": [
    {
      "text": "And honestly, I'm still figuring it out.",
      "start": 5.1,
      "end": 6.62,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "We've pumped out shorts,",
      "start": 6.7,
      "end": 7.52,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "paid ads,",
      "start": 7.84,
      "end": 8.46,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "onboarding videos, long form.",
      "start": 8.9,
      "end": 10.38,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "For a while,",
      "start": 10.44,
      "end": 10.84,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "I was trying",
      "start": 10.94,
      "end": 11.34,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "to do it all myself.",
      "start": 11.34,
      "end": 11.94,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "Different style every day,",
      "start": 12.24,
      "end": 13.22,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "one video a day.",
      "start": 13.4,
      "end": 14.38,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "It was unsustainable.",
      "start": 14.5,
      "end": 15.94,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "So we adjusted.",
      "start": 15.96,
      "end": 16.56,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "Now my boss handles",
      "start": 16.76,
      "end": 17.42,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "all the talking head content,",
      "start": 17.42,
      "end": 18.5,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "which is easier to produce",
      "start": 18.62,
      "end": 19.76,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "and a higher volume.",
      "start": 19.76,
      "end": 20.6,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "We outsource paid ads",
      "start": 20.76,
      "end": 21.82,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "to a team of editors while",
      "start": 21.82,
      "end": 23.1,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "I focus on the systems,",
      "start": 23.1,
      "end": 24.28,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "communications, and long form.",
      "start": 24.42,
      "end": 26.04,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "It's the first time it's",
      "start": 26.4,
      "end": 26.98,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "actually felt like a rhythm.",
      "start": 26.98,
      "end": 27.98,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm still building a full",
      "start": 27.98,
      "end": 29.0,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "content operating system,",
      "start": 29.0,
      "end": 30.32,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "pre-production all the way to analytics.",
      "start": 30.46,
      "end": 32.02,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "But sometimes it feels like",
      "start": 32.3,
      "end": 33.7,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm building the plane",
      "start": 33.7,
      "end": 34.54,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "as I'm flying it.",
      "start": 34.54,
      "end": 35.62,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "And I'm doing",
      "start": 35.72,
      "end": 36.06,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "this all in a city",
      "start": 36.06,
      "end": 37.06,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "that does not care",
      "start": 37.06,
      "end": 38.16,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "if you make it or not.",
      "start": 38.16,
      "end": 38.94,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "Walking through rats to get",
      "start": 39.04,
      "end": 40.32,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "to my apartment, missing my train,",
      "start": 40.32,
      "end": 42.1,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "or not being able",
      "start": 42.3,
      "end": 42.94,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "to sleep because of sirens.",
      "start": 42.94,
      "end": 44.14,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "That's just New York.",
      "start": 44.3,
      "end": 45.14,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "And I appreciate every second of it.",
      "start": 45.26,
      "end": 47.1,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "My boss and I are pleased",
      "start": 47.16,
      "end": 48.24,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "with the progress, but not satisfied.",
      "start": 48.24,
      "end": 49.86,
      "is_aroll": false
    },
    {
      "text": "I don't know if I'm",
      "start": 50.2,
      "end": 50.88,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "moving fast enough,",
      "start": 50.88,
      "end": 51.74,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "but I'm 42 days",
      "start": 51.92,
      "end": 52.9,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "in and I'm still here.",
      "start": 52.9,
      "end": 53.98,
      "is_aroll": true
    },
    {
      "text": "This is me documenting all of it.",
